ystok, his education in Petrograd, his formative years of involvement in filmmaking, his experiences during the Russian Civil War, and his interests in music, poetry and technology.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aMarxism.  aSoviet culture.  aavant-garde.  acinema.  acommunism.  adocumentary.  aexperimental art.  amedia studies.  apropaganda.  asound studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAcademic Studies Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311068818440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161811735940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781618117359423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781618117359.jpg  a978-3-11-068818-4  Academic Studies Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK